# Stadia Maps API key for the "Our reach" basemap.
# 1. Create a free account at https://client.stadiamaps.com/
# 2. Make a property, copy its API key, and paste it below (or set it in your
#    host's environment as VITE_STADIA_API_KEY).
# 3. For production, you can instead register your domain in the Stadia
#    dashboard and leave this blank — browser requests from that domain are
#    authenticated without a key.
VITE_STADIA_API_KEY=
